---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '@/components/sections/HeroSection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="FormX Smart Learning – Achieve Near-Perfect AI Accuracy"
  description=""
  canonicalUrl="https://www.formx.ai/products/smartadapt"
  showFooterForm={true}
>
  <HeroSection
    heading="Master Accuracy:&#x2028;Train Your AI with Real-World Corrections"
    subheading="Tired of static AI models that don't learn from your corrections? With FormX Smart Learning, your model learns from every review you make - so it gets smarter, faster."
    ctaPrimary={{ text: "Get Started ->", href: "/schedule-demo" }}
    bgClass="bg-f0f4f9"
    headingClass="product-hero-content-heading"
    subheadingClass="product-hero-content-subheading"
    image={{
      src: "/images/pages/products_instant-learning_kv.svg",
      alt: "",
      width: 515,
      height: 515,
    }}
  />

  <section>
    <div class="container-default logo-section w-container">
      <div class="text-block-50">Trusted by international companies</div>
      <div class="hero__llm__logowrap freeze">
        <ul role="list" class="logo-carousel freeze">
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="MTR">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="MTR" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-MTR@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="Google">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="Google" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-Google@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="Wilson Group">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="Wilson Group" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-WilsonGroup@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="LINK">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="LINK" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-LINK@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="Lika Hsin">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="Lika Hsin" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-LIKAHSIN@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="logo-carousel-item">
            <a href="#" class="logo-link w-inline-block" aria-label="Ayala Malls">
              <img width="150" loading="lazy" alt="Ayala Malls" src="/images/pages/homepage_logo-gray-AyalaMalls@2x.png" class="logo-image" />
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section product-section">
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <h2 class="product-2-block-heading mobile-center">How FormX Learns from&#x2028;Your Answers</h2>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph mobile-center">FormX Smart Learning gives you complete control over your AI's education. Whenever you correct or review an answer, our AI model retains that new information, becoming smarter and more accurate. By maintaining the right learning samples, you ensure your AI evolves in the direction that matters most to your business.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/products_smart-learning_how-FormX.svg" loading="lazy" width="343" height="300" alt="" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section product-section bg-f7f8fc">
    <div class="container-default heading-content w-container">
      <div class="home-heading">
        <h2 class="text-center">Get Started in 3 Easy Steps</h2>
      </div>
      <div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="_2-block-flex tabs-with-image w-tabs">
        <div class="hover-change tabs w-tab-menu">
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 1" data-w-id="8d1a38c1-fc5d-76e8-8431-82382f2ce242" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Define the Data Fields</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Specify which fields you want FormX to extract or interpret</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 2" data-w-id="8d1a38c1-fc5d-76e8-8431-82382f2ce247" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Upload the Sample</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Provide sample documents or data entries</div>
          </a>
          <a data-w-tab="Tab 3" data-w-id="8d1a38c1-fc5d-76e8-8431-82382f2ce24c" class="hover-change-content w-inline-block w-tab-link">
            <div class="hover-change-title">Review &amp; Correct</div>
            <div style="height:0px" class="hover-change-description">Inspect the AI's output, make adjustments as necessary, and confirm corrections. Your edits feed directly back into the model, improving future performance</div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="_2-block-flex-image tabs w-tab-content">
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
            <img width="600" sizes="100vw" alt="" src="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-1@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-1@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-1@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-1@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-1@2x.webp 1200w" class="radius-24" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="600" sizes="100vw" alt="" src="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-2@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-2@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-2@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-2@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-2@2x.webp 1200w" class="radius-24" />
          </div>
          <div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane">
            <img width="615" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 615px" alt="" src="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-3@2x.webp" loading="eager" srcset="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-3@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-3@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-3@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_get-started-3@2x.webp 1200w" class="radius-24" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section product-section">
    <h2 class="text-center">Two Ways to Improve your AI accuracy</h2>
    <div class="container-default w-container">
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <h3 class="product-2-block-heading3">Upload and label a few documents</h3>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">Rapidly boost accuracy by uploading a few samples with correct information. Great for setting up quickly or improving a specific type of document.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_continuouslearning@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="1370" height="1028" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_continuouslearning@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_continuouslearning@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_continuouslearning@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_continuouslearning@2x.webp 1370w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-2-block-wrapper reverse top-bottom-margin">
        <div class="product-2-block-text-wrapper">
          <h3 class="product-2-block-heading3">Improve accuracy as you use the extractors</h3>
          <div class="product-2-block-paragraph">Optionally, ask FormX to log the documents extracted, and use the API or Accuracy Centre to correct errors from the extractions. Over time, your model becomes more robust and handles documents similar to old one with better accuracy</div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-2-block-image-wrapper">
          <img src="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_instantlearning@2x.webp" loading="lazy" width="1370" height="1028" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" alt="" srcset="/images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_instantlearning@2x-p-500.webp 500w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_instantlearning@2x-p-800.webp 800w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_instantlearning@2x-p-1080.webp 1080w, /images/pages/products_instant-learning_two-way_instantlearning@2x.webp 1370w" class="_2-block-image-radius" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="bg-f7f8fc"></section>
</PageLayout>
